<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="HB0462" sponsor="Tiara Auxier" designation="HB" otherSponsor="David P. Hinkins" otherHouse="Senate" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL0883" date="2/24/2026 15:02:777" printDate="02-24 15:49" subVer="0" minVer="3" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>8</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="07/01/2026"><seclist><sect action="E" src="code" buid="2" uid="C53F-2-S402.5_2026070120260701" sort="53F02 04020520260701" mtype="section" effdate="07/01/2026">53F-2-402.5</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="approp" buid="6" uid="APP2027" sort="UP0002027" mtype="uncod" effdate="07/01/2026"/><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="7" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="07/01/2026"/></seclist></aminfo><amendinfo level="1"/><aminfo anum="-1" effdate="07/01/2026"><seclist><sect action="E" src="code" buid="2" uid="C53F-2-S402.5_2026070120260701" sort="53F02 04020520260701" mtype="section" effdate="07/01/2026">53F-2-402.5</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="approp" buid="6" uid="APP2027" sort="UP0002027" mtype="uncod" effdate="07/01/2026"/><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="7" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="07/01/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">School Bus Internet Access</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Tiara Auxier</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>Senate Sponsor: David P. Hinkins</otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill creates a grant program to provide internet connectivity on school buses in rural <ln numlevel="1" lineno="6" slineno="0-6"/>school districts.</gd><hphead lineno="7">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="1">defines terms;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10" level="1">creates a grant program for rural school districts to install and operate internet <ln numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11"/>connectivity systems on school buses;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="12" slineno="0-12" level="1">establishes priority criteria for awarding grants;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13" level="1">allows districts to combine grant money with district funds;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="14" slineno="0-14" level="1">requires grant recipients to commit to long-term operation of internet connectivity <ln numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15"/>systems; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16" level="1">requires the State Board of Education to make rules for grant administration.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17" display="normal">Money Appropriated in this Bill:<fy fy="2027" ltid="2" seq="2027" numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18"><ltcat ltid="3" seq="1">This bill appropriates <ltamt>$325,000</ltamt> in operating and capital budgets for fiscal year 2027, all of <ln numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19"/>which is from the various sources as detailed in this bill.</ltcat></fy></moni><oc numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="0-20">Other Special Clauses:<ocl type="effdate" sort="2" numlevel="1" lineno="21" slineno="0-21">This bill provides a special effective date.</ocl></oc><sa numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="0-22">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saent numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="0-23"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="53F-2-402.5" src="code" uid="C53F-2-S402.5_2026070120260701" buid="2" sort="53F02 04020520260701" numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="0-24"><bold>53F-2-402.5</bold>, Utah Code Annotated 1953</sn></saent></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="25"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="0-26">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="2" num="53F-2-402.5" type="enact" src="code" uid="C53F-2-S402.5_2026070120260701" sort="53F02 04020520260701" numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-2" number="53F-2-402.5" type="enact"><secline lineno="27">Section 1. Section <bold>53F-2-402.5</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><catline lineno="28"><bold>53F-2-402.5<parens/>. Rural school district transportation grants.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="2-1" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-3" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1000" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="7" groupid="5" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">As used in this section:</amend><subsection ssid="2-10" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-4" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="151" groupid="9" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"Eligible school" means a public school within a school district:</amend><subsection ssid="2-42" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-5" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="156" groupid="13" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">located in a county of the fourth, fifth, or sixth class, as defined in Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="17-50-501"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-6"/>17-50-501</xref>; or</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-43" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-7" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="161" groupid="17" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">with fewer than 3,000 students enrolled in the school district.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="2-44" dnum="_-o:b-i:_-HF" numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-8" ea="erase" anum="-1" owner="HF" style="7" level="2" chamber="HF"><display><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="1004" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="509" groupid="290" style="7" owner="HF" level="1">"</amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="510" groupid="291" style="7" owner="HF" level="1">Extended trip</amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="511" groupid="292" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" deltag="end">" means a school bus trip to a school-sponsored <ln numlevel="2" lineno="34a" slineno="1-8a"/>event, including an </amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="535" groupid="316" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-9"/></amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="512" groupid="293" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="both" deltag="both">athletic competition, academic competition, or club activity, that requires a student in </amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="536" groupid="317" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-10"/></amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="513" groupid="294" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="both">grades 7 through 12 to travel more than 60 minutes one-way.</amend><amendoutend style="7"/></subsection><subsection ssid="2-47" dnum="_-o:c-i:b-HF" numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-11" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="1005" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" deltag="both">(c)</amend><amendoutend style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="-1" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" amendtag="start" space="true">(b)</amend><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="180" groupid="30" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"Rural school district" means a school district that operates one or more <ln numlevel="2" lineno="37a" slineno="1-11a"/>eligible <ln numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-12"/>schools.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="2-48" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-13" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="181" groupid="31" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" endid="541" base="true" amendtag="end">Subject to legislative appropriations, the state board shall distribute grant money to rural <ln numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-14"/>school districts to install and operate internet connectivity systems on school buses</amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="514" groupid="295" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="both" deltag="both"> <ln numlevel="2" lineno="40a" slineno="1-14a"/>used </amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="538" groupid="319" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="1-15"/></amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="515" groupid="296" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="start">for </amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="516" groupid="297" style="7" owner="HF" level="1">extended trip</amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="517" groupid="298" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" deltag="end">s</amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="541" groupid="322" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both">.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-49" dnum="_-o:3-i" numlevel="1" lineno="42" slineno="1-16" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1007" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(3)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="188" groupid="36" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">A rural school district may apply to the state board for a grant under this section.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-50" dnum="_-o:4-i" numlevel="1" lineno="43" slineno="1-17" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1008" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(4)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="193" groupid="40" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The state board may award a grant to a rural school district that:</amend><subsection ssid="2-51" dnum="_-o:a-i:_-HF" numlevel="1" lineno="44" slineno="1-18" ea="erase" anum="-1" owner="HF" style="7" level="2" chamber="HF"><display><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="1009" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="518" groupid="299" style="7" owner="HF" level="1">operates one or more school bus routes that qualify as </amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="519" groupid="300" style="7" owner="HF" level="1">extended trip</amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="520" groupid="301" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" deltag="end"><ln numlevel="2" lineno="44a" slineno="1-18a"/>s under </amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="544" groupid="325" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="45" slineno="1-19"/></amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="521" groupid="302" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="both">Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="53F-2-402.5(1)(b)">(1)(b)</xref>;</amend><amendoutend style="7"/></subsection><subsection ssid="2-52" dnum="_-o:b-i:a-HF" numlevel="1" lineno="46" slineno="1-20" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="1010" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" deltag="both">(b)</amend><amendoutend style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="amend" pairid="1011" style="-1" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" amendtag="start" space="true">(a)</amend><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="203" groupid="48" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">submits an application in accordance with state board rule; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-53" dnum="_-o:c-i:b-HF" numlevel="1" lineno="47" slineno="1-21" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="1011" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="both">(c)</amend><amendoutend style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="amend" pairid="1012" style="-1" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" amendtag="start" space="true">(b)</amend><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="208" groupid="52" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">agrees to the requirements in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="53F-2-402.5(7)">(7)</xref>.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="2-54" dnum="_-o:5-i" numlevel="1" lineno="48" slineno="1-22" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1012" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(5)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="334" groupid="147" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" endid="549" base="true" amendtag="end">In awarding grants under this section, the state board shall give preference to rural <ln numlevel="1" lineno="49" slineno="1-23"/>school districts that do not currently have internet connectivity systems on school buses</amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="522" groupid="303" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="both" deltag="both"> </amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="546" groupid="327" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="50" slineno="1-24"/></amend><houseStart display="true"/><houseFloorStart/><amendoutstart style="7"/><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="523" groupid="304" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="start" deltag="start">used for </amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="524" groupid="305" style="7" owner="HF" level="1">extended trip</amend><amend anum="-1" ea="erase" pairid="525" groupid="306" style="7" owner="HF" level="1" hftag="end" deltag="end">s</amend><amendoutend style="7"/><houseFloorEnd/><houseEnd display="true"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="549" groupid="330" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" base="true" amendtag="both">.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-93" dnum="_-o:6-i" numlevel="1" lineno="51" slineno="1-25" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1013" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(6)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="387" groupid="189" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">Notwithstanding Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="53F-2-402.5(5)">(5)</xref>:</amend><subsection ssid="2-94" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="52" slineno="1-26" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1014" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="392" groupid="193" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">subject to legislative appropriations, the state board shall ensure each eligible rural <ln numlevel="1" lineno="53" slineno="1-27"/>school district receives funding for at least two school buses; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-84" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="54" slineno="1-28" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1015" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="341" groupid="152" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">the state board may not award a grant to a district in an amount that exceeds the total <ln numlevel="1" lineno="55" slineno="1-29"/>cost to:</amend><subsection ssid="2-85" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="56" slineno="1-30" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1016" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="346" groupid="156" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">retrofit two school buses with internet connectivity systems; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="2-86" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="57" slineno="1-31" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1017" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="351" groupid="160" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">pay for internet connectivity services for two school buses for one year.</amend></subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="2-55" dnum="_-o:7-i" numlevel="1" lineno="58" slineno="1-32" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1018" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(7)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="216" groupid="58" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">A rural school district that receives a grant under this section shall:</amend><subsection ssid="2-56" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="59" slineno="1-33" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1019" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="221" groupid="62" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">use grant money to:</amend><subsection ssid="2-57" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="60" slineno="1-34" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1020" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="226" groupid="66" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">retrofit school buses with internet 