.</number><display display="true">Operating and Capital Budgets</display><summary numlevel="1" lineno="102" slineno="2-6">Under the terms and conditions of Title 63J, Chapter 1, Budgetary Procedures Act, the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="103" slineno="2-7"/>Legislature appropriates the following sums of money from the funds or accounts indicated for <ln numlevel="1" lineno="104" slineno="2-8"/>the use and support of the government of the state of Utah.</summary><committee nodeid="4" name="Public Education" seq="70"><display display="false">PUBLIC EDUCATION</display><agency nodeid="5" seq="29140000" name="State Board of Education"><display display="false">STATE BOARD OF EDUCATION</display><lineitem seq="29143000" nodeid="6" name="Contracted Initiatives and Grants" numlevel="1" lineno="105" slineno="2-9"><display display="true">ITEM 1</display><lidesc>State Board of Education - Contracted Initiatives and Grants</lidesc><sources><appsrc name="Public Education Economic Stabilization Restricted Account" srcid="8" seq="3030.1" onetime="true" numlevel="1" lineno="106" slineno="2-10"><display display="true">From Public Education Economic Stabilization <ln numlevel="1" lineno="107" slineno="2-11"/>Restricted Account, One-time</display><amt>325,000</amt></appsrc></sources><programs numlevel="1" lineno="108" slineno="2-12" display="true"><program name="Contracts and Grants" dstid="7" seq="29143008" numlevel="1" lineno="109" slineno="2-13"><display display="true">Contracts and Grants</display><pamt>325,000</pamt></program></programs><authorizations hide="true"/></lineitem></agency></committee></licat></sectionText></section></bsec><bsec buid="7" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="110" slineno="3-1" sn="3"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="110">Section 3.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="111"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="7/1/2026">July 1, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>2-24-26 3:49 PM</tm></rev></foot></leg>